<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Iniciar sesión | SGER</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, 'Noto Sans', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, #f8fafc 0%, #f6f7fb 100%);
            color: #111827;
        }

        .auth-container {
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            align-items: center;
            justify-items: center;
            /* centra los elementos en el eje horizontal */
            padding: 32px 24px;
        }

        @media (min-width: 900px) {
            .auth-container {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr 420px;
                gap: 40px;
                padding: 48px 64px;
                align-items: center;
                /* asegura centrado vertical en desktop */
                justify-items: center;
                /* asegura centrado horizontal en desktop */
            }
        }

        /* Centrar la tarjeta de login */
        .auth-container>section:last-child {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            justify-self: center;
            /* centra ese item dentro de la celda del grid */
            width: 100%;
        }

        .brand {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            color: #1f2937;
        }

        .logo {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            background: #1f2937;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: #fff;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .hero {
            max-width: 720px;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 32px;
            line-height: 1.2;
            margin: 0 0 12px;
            color: #0f172a;
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #6b7280;
            margin: 0 0 24px;
        }

        .callouts {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 12px;
        }

        .callout {
            background: #fff;
            border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 14px;
            box-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
            color: #374151;
        }

        .card {
            background: #fff;
            border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(31, 41, 55, 0.12);
            max-width: 420px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .card h4 {
            color: #111827;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .subtle-label {
            margin: 8px 0 10px;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #6b7280;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 8px;
            padding: 8px 12px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            background: #fff;
            color: #111827;
            width: auto;
            text-align: center;
            transition: transform 0.08s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #f3f4f6;
            border-color: #d1d5db;
            transform: translateY(-1px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
        }

        .btn-google {
            background: transparent;
            color: #ea4335;
            border-color: #ea4335;
            display: flex;
            /* block-level flex for centering with margin auto */
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            width: fit-content;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .btn-google:hover {
            background-color: #f3f4f6;
            color: #ea4335;
            border-color: #ea4335;
        }

        .btn-google:active {
            background-color: #ea4335;
            color: #fff;
            border-color: #ea4335;
        }

        .btn-google svg {
            width: 16px;
            height: 16px;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .legal {
            margin-top: 12px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #6b7280;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="auth-container">
        <section class="hero">
            <div class="brand">
                <div class="logo">S</div>
                <strong>SGER</strong>
            </div>
            <h1>Bienvenido a SGER</h1>
            <p>Gestiona usuarios, repartidores y pedidos en un panel moderno y organizado.
                Inicia sesión para acceder a tu panel de control.</p>
            <div class="callouts">
                <div class="callout">• Lista y detalle de pedidos</div>
                <div class="callout">• Asignación de zonas y repartidores</div>
                <div class="callout">• Administración de usuarios</div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section>
            <div class="card">
                <h4>Iniciar sesión</h4>
                <div class="subtle-label">Iniciar con</div>
                <a href="/auth/google" class="btn btn-google">
